OL,3,CRight to remove former Prince's
OL,4,Cplaque, says top royal representative
OL,6,FA plaque which displayed the name of
OL,7,Fthe former Prince Andrew has been
OL,8,Fremoved from St Helier's Elizabeth
OL,9,FMarina.
OL,11,FPorts of Jersey requested that the
OL,12,Fcommemorative stone be changed, with
OL,13,Fapproval coming from the Royal
OL,14,FHousehold via Government House.
OL,16,FIt was placed there to mark the former
OL,17,FPrince's official opening of the
OL,18,FMarina at Castle Quay on 15 May 1998.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/6
