PN,38402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1777558269
OL,3,CRight to remove former Prince's
OL,4,Cplaque, says top royal representative
OL,6,FThe plaque has now been replaced with
OL,7,Fone that reads: "Opened on behalf of
OL,8,FHer Majesty Queen Elizabeth II", with
OL,9,Fthe same date.
OL,11,FThe Monarch's official representative
OL,12,Fin Jersey, Lieutenant-Governor Vice
OL,13,FAdmiral Sir Jerry Kyd, has told ITV
OL,14,FNews that it was the right decision to
OL,15,Falter the wording, while stating that
OL,16,Fties between Crown Dependencies such
OL,17,Fas Jersey and the Royal Family are
OL,18,F"unbreakable".
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/6
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1777558269
OL,3,CRight to remove former Prince's
OL,4,Cplaque, says top royal representative
OL,6,FHis Excellency adds: "It's absolutely
OL,7,Fappropriate that the plaque has been
OL,8,Fadjusted.
OL,10,F"Institutions like the Royal Family,
OL,11,Fthe armed forces and the courts are so
OL,12,Fessential for the welfare and
OL,13,Fprosperity of our democratic system."
OL,15,FAndrew Mountbatten-Windsor had several
OL,16,Fconnections to the Channel Islands,
OL,17,Fincluding serving as patron of the
OL,18,FRoyal Jersey Golf Club and the
OL,19,FAlderney Maritime Trust.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/6
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
