FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1777558269
OL,3,CRight to remove former Prince's
OL,4,Cplaque, says top royal representative
OL,6,FAll of his royal patronages were
OL,7,Freturned to the Queen in 2022.
OL,9,FThe decision to remove the plaque at
OL,10,FElizabeth Marina follows the former
OL,11,FPrince being stripped of his royal
OL,12,Ftitles due to his association with the
OL,13,Fconvicted paedophile and American
OL,14,Ffinancier Jeffrey Epstein.
OL,16,FIn a statement released by the Royal
OL,17,FFamily at the time, they said: "These
OL,18,Fcensures are deemed necessary,
OL,19,Fnotwithstanding the fact that he
OL,20,Fcontinues to deny the allegations
OL,21,Fagainst him."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/6
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
