PN,38405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1777558269
OL,3,CRight to remove former Prince's
OL,4,Cplaque, says top royal representative
OL,6,FIn October, Jersey's most senior
OL,7,Flawyer, Bailiff Robert MacRae, said:
OL,8,F"Decisions regarding royal titles rest
OL,9,Fwith His Majesty The King and the
OL,10,FRoyal Household, and Jersey will
OL,11,Fcontinue to follow their guidance on
OL,12,Fmatters arising from the announcement."
OL,14,FAndrew has always denied any
OL,15,Fwrongdoing.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/6
